> "Lord Elder, I've reached the shuttle and I'm now performing preliminary take off proceedures."

As Quickstride finished the take off procedures, the door to the
shuttle bay slid open as Lord Elder entered. he looked over the
controls as he nodded in satisfaction, "Good. All is in readiness."
With a deft touch Lord Elder laid in the coordinates and entered the
security codes that would open the doors to the outside world.

With a huge click and rumble the Ark doors slowly slid open to allow
sunlight and various bits of debris to enter into the room. For a
moment the outer shield flickered as it opened a hole, just large
enough for the shuttle to pass through, one that would close as they
exited it.

Lord Elder looked over at Quickstride, "Take us out young Maximal. Let
us see how much of a distraction we can be. When we get there we can
fire on the base, hopefully that will give Rat Trap and the Autobot
Tuscon and window of opportunity to escape."

(TAG)

OOC: Feel free to utilize the shuttle if you folks can't wait till Monday :)

Preston
(Lord Elder)
